            </quote>; and</text>
				</paragraph>
        <paragraph id="H3104F9E597244BC289313635DACDCBA7">
					<enum>(4)</enum>
					<text>in <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Horse Protection Act/s:5/p:6">paragraph (6)</cato:entity-ref>—</text>
